  "body": "### Added\r\n- Added support for MIFARE Classic cards (1K and 4K) with PC/SC compliant authentication:\r\n  - New `prepareMifareClassicAuthenticate(int blockAddress, MifareClassicKeyType keyType, byte[] key)` method to load and authenticate with a MIFARE Classic key.\r\n  - New `prepareMifareClassicAuthenticate(int blockAddress, MifareClassicKeyType keyType, int keyNumber)` method to authenticate using a previously loaded key.\r\n  - Available in both `StorageCardSelectionExtension` and `StorageCardTransactionManager` interfaces.\r\n- Added ST25-specific methods to replace deprecated generic system block methods:\r\n  - `prepareSt25ReadSystemBlock()` for reading ST25/SRT512 system blocks.\r\n  - `prepareSt25WriteSystemBlock(byte[] data)` for writing ST25/SRT512 system blocks.\r\n### Deprecated\r\n- Deprecated `prepareReadSystemBlock()` in favor of `prepareSt25ReadSystemBlock()`.\r\n- Deprecated `prepareWriteSystemBlock(byte[] data)` in favor of `prepareSt25WriteSystemBlock(byte[] data)`.).\r\n### Upgraded\r\n- `keypop-storagecard-java-api` from `1.0.0` to `1.1.0`\r\n- `keyple-util-java-lib` from `2.4.0` to `2.4.1`\r\n- `slf4j-api` from `1.7.32` to `1.7.36` (compileOnly)"
